SELECT [t].[QuizId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[QuestionCount], [t].[ShowCase], [t].[Title], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[CorrectOptionId], [t0].[Order], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[QuizId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[IsCorrect], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[QuestionId0]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [q].[QuizId], [q].[CreatedDate], [q].[QuestionCount], [q].[ShowCase], [q].[Title], [q].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Quizzes] AS [q]
    WHERE [q].[QuizId] = @__quizId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q0].[QuestionId], [q0].[CorrectOptionId], [q0].[Order], [q0].[QuestionText], [q0].[QuizId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[IsCorrect], [o].[OptionText], [o].[QuestionId] AS [QuestionId0]
    FROM [Questions] AS [q0]
    LEFT JOIN [Options] AS [o] ON [q0].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
